459
00:58:14,205 --> 00:58:16,771
Idemo. Otvori vatru!

460
00:58:22,675 --> 00:58:24,050
Otvori vatru!

461
00:58:25,395 --> 00:58:26,681
Otvori vatru!

462
00:59:28,849 --> 00:59:30,815
Uništeni su topovi
sa Kitakuba.

463
00:59:31,032 --> 00:59:33,246
